Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve

After talking with Alex offline, he pointed out that that this might happen in cases when there is import within the same namespace twice:

for example:

...
    import a.b.c
    import a.b.c.d as e
...

might be an issue

however, just

...
    import a.b.c.d as e
...

should be fine.
